M|yvon-pl-runway|Runway = Current Cash / |Net Monthly Burn|
M|yvon-pl-runway|Net Burn = Total OpEx - Total Operating Income
M|yvon-pl-runway|```
M|yvon-pl-runway|| Runway | Level | Action |
M|yvon-pl-runway||--------|-------|--------|
M|yvon-pl-runway|| More than 12 months | Stable | Continue normal operations |
M|yvon-pl-runway|| 6 to 12 months | Watch | Flag to Diana, rv discretionary spend |
M|yvon-pl-runway|| 4 to 6 months | Alert | Surface to Marcus immediately, cost rv required |
M|yvon-pl-runway|| 2 to 4 months | Critical | Urgent action: reduce burn, accelerate revenue |
M|yvon-pl-runway|| Less than 2 months | Emergency | All hands: survival mode |
M|yvon-pl-runway|```
