M|yvon-pl-runway|1. **Week 1:** Close prior month P&L for both ventures
M|yvon-pl-runway|2. **Week 1:** Calculate runway, update Felix's tracking sheet
M|yvon-pl-runway|3. **Week 1:** If runway changed category, alert Marcus
M|yvon-pl-runway|4. **Week 2:** rv discretionary spend against budget
M|yvon-pl-runway|5. **End of Month:** Consolidate view sent to Marcus